{"tid":2319813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN：第一夫人梅蘭妮亞已經開始打包  準備開始她離開白宮後的新生活","createTime":"2020-12-10T10:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T03:30:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"79f2d924d2892b30e5673946db1babc0ce663de1","tid":2319813,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"川普到現在還不願意放棄，承認敗選。不過根據美國有線電視新聞網CNN報導，第一夫人梅蘭妮亞，已經開始打包，甚至在幫兒子選學校，她已經往前看，準備開始她離開白宮後的新生活。<br />\n<br />\n美國第一夫人梅蘭妮亞(2020.12.5)說：「川普總統每一天都在為你們奮鬥。」美國總統川普，滿面笑容，看著賢內助在台上支持著他，川普還不願意放棄，希望奇蹟出現，選舉結果大逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n但根據美國有線電視新聞網CNN的報導，梅蘭妮亞已經開始打包準備搬家。CNN駐白宮記者班尼特：「她已經在白宮打包，確定哪件家具要運去哪，她也在考慮佛州的學校，未來她兒子要上哪一間學校。」<br />\n<br />\n而且梅蘭妮亞在7號宣布，白宮網球休閒館完工，她在推特上發文表示，希望這個私人空間，能夠成為未來第一家庭的休閒場所，外界認為未來的第一家庭是誰，不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n不只梅蘭妮亞千頭萬緒，女兒伊凡卡也在思考未來。記者說：「第一家庭的女兒與她的夫婿，剛剛買下這塊靠海的土地，要價三千萬美元，這邊位於邁阿密比斯坎灣的印度溪島，是美國最昂貴的社區。」<br />\n<br />\n這邊是名副其實的超級富人島，島上的住戶包括超模利瑪，還有麥克法森，而且這邊距離川普的海湖度假莊園，開車不用1個小時，再加上伊凡卡的小叔約書亞，今年也在邁阿密買房，看來川普一家，明年會在陽光普照的佛州，好好享受新生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/202012/202012102023672.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Finternational%2F202012%2F202012102023672.html&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=3bde89e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/202012/202012102023672.html</a>"},{"pid":"bcec7b0707020d3c5cee6f72942734b77e7dc522","tid":2319813,"uid":251732,"like":138,"dislike":5,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"6e470de91b2c79409d76fc1269efca2dd62104f1","tid":2319813,"uid":256246,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"2024搬返返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a76f6f7bfa8d7fa2b9d2c99ca47daa446a17c67","tid":2319813,"uid":78295,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分分鐘到時Pelosi上任一陣<br />\n打包都正常"},{"pid":"89e3f2d230e9208f54b7c2a3ed881eda60c6b787","tid":2319813,"uid":256019,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"又係CNN，睇黎繼Facebook後，好快被清算！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be57dd6027caad85f9c1c9a675c4eb141cc4c91c","tid":2319813,"uid":276273,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"XiNN"},{"pid":"62746fec8b14b31eb9d94e59dddeeffc310f3093","tid":2319813,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6e470de91b2c79409d76fc1269efca2dd62104f1","tid":2319813,"uid":256246,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"2024搬返返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"I will be back<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a280857972b2aeae356ac4db9c3af418825a24","tid":2319813,"uid":18569,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"CNN報到冇野好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15935266749fc6f7053c04f841a55fce40c355e2","tid":2319813,"uid":73600,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"睇到CNN既反應: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee90cee15c6f5409098f60a93eee120b1660eeb","tid":2319813,"uid":122275,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"馬英九睇手錶"},{"pid":"5697e9916cc61c40815a5c7cb5b448dede15dbb9","tid":2319813,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":